## ததஅக

[ cōṭacōpacāram ]  
  
பெ. ṣōḍaša + upacāra. the sixteen acts ofhomage and honour paid to deities and venerable personages  
viz.  
ācaṉam  
cuvākatam  
pāttiyam  
arkkiyam  
